mainText: Jan 2 Kate Spade Pink Feather Clutch I saw this clutch at Kate Spade a long time ago and fell immediately in love! How can you resist such a gorgeous accessory with flowing ostrich feathers, the perfect shade of pink, and the gold details? The only issue was $400 didn't seem like a reasonable price for a clutch I would only use occasionally- I tend to invest in basics that I know I will get plenty of use out of. Even after all this time, it was still an image in the back of my head. Luckily, I stumbled across this beauty from Asos, on sale for only $28- I mean come on, there was no way I was walking away from that! Click the link below to add this to your closet before its gone!
